description: Early life stage sample of Montipora capitata offspring fertilized from wildtype gametes collected in Kaneohe Bay, Oahu, Hawaii coral reef environment. Early life stages reared in flow-through laboratory tank systems at ambient conditions sampled by preservation in RNA/DNA shield across ontogeny.
